{"tid":1351874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[請置頂]光復元朗路線！","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:31:26.000Z","uid":126231,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca490311d36e4e67a8f044db05156f965aacaef","tid":1351874,"uid":126231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔知應該同邊個講<br />\n但極度建議由元朗運動場走步<br />\n途經元朗警署<br />\n之後一直經大馬路向東行<br />\n去yoho下面鄉紳委員會建築<br />\n再向yoho及新元朗中心方向<br />\n向南邊圍方向<br />\n到達南邊圍作為終點</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔知可以同邊個作出尼個建議<br />\n大家認為好既請幫手推下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更希望係可以星期六出發<br />\n唔洗掛住星期一要番工</span>"},{"pid":"c4bf8d97427bbbcfdc35f6f8fcf7d080ede22075","tid":1351874,"uid":15548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"光乜鳩呀，西鐵站直去南邊圍啦"},{"pid":"d60ba73dc68074ef9e79083b1d8d50d7945cbf95","tid":1351874,"uid":126231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"Skip元朗警署好咩？"},{"pid":"8c1e5d05589740584e7913cd87f20f800b4d7a89","tid":1351874,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/299ScJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F299ScJM.png&h=495f8d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTpiSJN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTpiSJN.png&h=3e77bd63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OosHzW7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOosHzW7.png&h=5182388e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7RUq3O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7RUq3O.png&h=64d84eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WQEOvvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQEOvvt.png&h=037dce4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0eac0a13cd8c03e3ccca0e4